description: The home features private entry copper-clad door leading to salon with marble floors. Stunning great room has soaring 45 foot ceilings with glass windows, polished concrete floors, exposed brick & sculptural steel beams. The chef's kitchen has honed granite counters, high-end S/S appliances, French cabinets & gas range.
